value: * This script contains the code to merge the discounted network variables needed for the script "creating_discounted_prod_sample.do" of the on-line appendix in Ductor, L., Fafchamps, M., Goyal S. and M. van der Leij. Social Networks and Research Output. The Review of Economics and Statistics.
* Important: before running this script, you need to obtain all the discounted network variables running the script "Allnetworkvariables_dt.R".
